text: Akuoma Ugo Tracy Omeoga is a Nigerian bobsledder from USA. Omeoga competed at the 2018 Winter Olympics. She was born on 22 June 1992.Akuoma Omeoga == References == Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:American bobsledders Category:Olympians for Nigeria Category:Sportspeople from Saint Paul, Minnesota
